1
00:01:04,959 --> 00:01:06,420
Kneel for the whole night.

2
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:08,660
Kneel down.

3
00:01:09,240 --> 00:01:09,840
Hurry up.

4
00:01:10,039 --> 00:01:10,520
Kneel.

5
00:01:10,520 --> 00:01:11,480
Kneel before me.

6
00:01:12,960 --> 00:01:13,760
Kneel down.

7
00:01:14,080 --> 00:01:14,720
Kneel.

8
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:34,360
Why are you here all alone, admiring yourself, Sister?

9
00:01:34,360 --> 00:01:36,120
If you dare take another step,

10
00:01:36,479 --> 00:01:38,160
I'll make sure you never walk again.

11
00:01:38,160 --> 00:01:39,160
Sister,

12
00:01:39,160 --> 00:01:42,680
you've heard that Bai Manchuan is getting married, right?

13
00:01:45,520 --> 00:01:47,880
That Bai Manchuan really is too much.

14
00:01:47,880 --> 00:01:50,400
He knows how you feel about him,

15
00:01:50,479 --> 00:01:53,120
yet he didn't even send an invitation for his wedding.

16
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:55,640
How heartless.

17
00:01:56,960 --> 00:01:59,890
But I heard Marquis Bai likes his new bride very much.

18
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:03,080
Even the Third Prince is officiating the wedding.

19
00:02:03,080 --> 00:02:05,680
Love can never be forced.

20
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:08,080
Stop pretending, Sister.

21
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:09,840
I know you're jealous.

22
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:14,080
It's a pity Song Xuan is the legitimate daughter of the General's Manor,

23
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:17,640
while you are just an illegitimate daughter.

24
00:02:17,640 --> 00:02:19,800
You traveled all the way to the capital to find your father.

25
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:21,530
Who knows what happened to you.

26
00:02:32,320 --> 00:02:34,850
Didn't you say you'd take me to find my father?

27
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:36,320
Find your father?

28
00:02:36,320 --> 00:02:37,960
We have plenty of daddies here.

29
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:38,880
Look at us two brothers.

30
00:02:38,880 --> 00:02:39,640
Why don't you pick one?

31
00:02:39,640 --> 00:02:41,040
Or both of us together?

32
00:02:41,040 --> 00:02:42,280
We guarantee you'll be satisfied.

33
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:43,360
What do you want?

34
00:02:44,480 --> 00:02:46,079
Where do you think you're going?

35
00:02:46,079 --> 00:02:49,000
Everyone knows Prime Minister Shen only has one daughter.

36
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:50,800
Where did a wild brat like you come from?

37
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:52,480
You dare trick us brothers?

38
00:02:52,480 --> 00:02:53,960
Let go of me.

39
00:02:54,040 --> 00:02:55,320
You are committing a grave offense.

40
00:02:55,320 --> 00:02:56,000
If my father finds out,

41
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:57,060
he won't spare you.

42
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:58,240
An offense?

43
00:02:58,280 --> 00:02:59,560
You're all alone now.

44
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:00,840
Who cares about you?

45
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:03,040
Let me go! Let me go!

46
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:06,320
Help!

47
00:03:06,320 --> 00:03:07,120
Behave yourself.

48
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:08,040
Let me go.

49
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:10,200
Stay still.

50
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:12,040
Stop.

51
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:17,800
I thought the girls in Baihua Tower were all willing.

52
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:18,420
How come

53
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:20,400
someone is being forced?

54
00:03:20,400 --> 00:03:21,160
Who are you?

55
00:03:21,160 --> 00:03:22,360
You have a death wish?

56
00:03:27,320 --> 00:03:31,000
There is no business in this capital that I, Bai Manchuan, dare not meddle in.

57
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:33,160
Kid, do you know who we are?

58
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:35,290
I don't care who you are.

59
00:03:35,840 --> 00:03:39,440
Everyone knows Baihua Tower never forces women into prostitution.

60
00:03:39,440 --> 00:03:42,240
How dare lowlifes like you bring people here!

61
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,610
Are you tired of living?

62
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:45,970
Wait, aren't you...

63
00:03:47,079 --> 00:03:48,360
I'm leaving right now.

64
00:03:48,760 --> 00:03:50,360
You know what's good for you.

65
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:50,960
Go.

66
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:10,000
Mother.

67
00:04:13,320 --> 00:04:14,120
My child.

68
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:17,360
Go find Prime Minister Shen Zhao.

69
00:04:18,640 --> 00:04:20,839
He is your biological father.

70
00:04:21,040 --> 00:04:23,000
Let's go together.

71
00:04:25,640 --> 00:04:27,880
This is the only thing my mother left me.

72
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:33,800
No one at the Prime Minister's Manor pays attention to you.

73
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:36,260
Come on, I'll take you to claim your kinship.

74
00:04:36,400 --> 00:04:37,560
Trust me.

75
00:04:37,960 --> 00:04:40,520
Although I, Bai Manchuan, have a bad reputation,

76
00:04:40,520 --> 00:04:42,920
I'm actually a good person.

77
00:04:59,159 --> 00:05:00,240
What do you want?

78
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:04,040
There is nothing I want that I cannot get.

79
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:06,420
You want to be Bai Manchuan's concubine?

80
00:05:07,560 --> 00:05:10,800
Too bad the Bai family forbids concubines.

81
00:05:10,840 --> 00:05:12,700
The Song family is even stricter.

82
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:16,960
I wouldn't let Bai Manchuan take a concubine anyway.

83
00:05:16,960 --> 00:05:18,040
You're crazy.

84
00:05:23,640 --> 00:05:27,080
It's getting cold. Time to make myself a pair of gloves.

85
00:05:30,960 --> 00:05:31,480
Son.

86
00:05:34,680 --> 00:05:36,200
Why am I tied to the bed?

87
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:37,120
Son.

88
00:05:37,800 --> 00:05:40,600
Today is your big day.

89
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:42,520
No! I refuse!

90
00:05:42,520 --> 00:05:44,240
Do you agree now?

91
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:46,040
It's not up to you.

92
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:48,120
No! Let me go!

93
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:49,080
You two, come here.

94
00:05:49,080 --> 00:05:50,360
Tighten the ropes.

95
00:05:50,720 --> 00:05:51,450
Stop moving.

96
00:05:52,080 --> 00:05:53,080
Father, I refuse!

97
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:56,200
Father, have mercy!

98
00:05:56,360 --> 00:05:57,040
Don't be in such a rush.

99
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:57,880
Brother.

100
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:59,400
Sister, help me!

101
00:05:59,400 --> 00:06:00,120
Stop struggling.

102
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:01,760
You brought this on yourself.

103
00:06:01,760 --> 00:06:02,360
Right, Father?

104
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:02,920
Zhaohua.

105
00:06:02,920 --> 00:06:03,880
Just in time.

106
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:05,480
I have an important task for you.

107
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:08,280
Dress your brother up nicely today.

108
00:06:08,680 --> 00:06:10,540
Don't let the Bai Manor lose face.

109
00:06:10,680 --> 00:06:11,960
Don't worry, Father.

110
00:06:13,120 --> 00:06:15,520
I'll make sure Brother looks sharp.

111
00:06:15,520 --> 00:06:16,400
He won't embarrass the Marquis Manor.

112
00:06:16,400 --> 00:06:17,120
Good.

113
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:19,200
I'll go pick up the bride.

114
00:06:19,200 --> 00:06:20,400
This is forced marriage.

115
00:06:20,400 --> 00:06:20,960
No.

116
00:06:20,960 --> 00:06:21,560
Forced wedlock.

117
00:06:21,560 --> 00:06:21,960
No.

118
00:06:21,960 --> 00:06:23,600
Coercing an innocent man.

119
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:24,920
Innocent man?

120
00:06:25,960 --> 00:06:26,480
Son.

121
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:28,080
Coming from you,

122
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:29,680
that sounds a bit rich.

123
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:31,760
I don't care! I won't give in!

124
00:06:31,960 --> 00:06:33,000
Let me go!

125
00:06:34,760 --> 00:06:35,280
Take him away.

126
00:06:35,280 --> 00:06:35,810
Yes, sir.

127
00:06:46,159 --> 00:06:47,000
Third Prince.

128
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:48,080
Lord Shen.

129
00:06:48,280 --> 00:06:49,760
What brings you two here?

130
00:06:49,760 --> 00:06:53,040
Your Highness, it seems Marquis Bai doesn't welcome you.

131
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:54,360
Welcome. Welcome.

132
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:55,520
How could I not?

133
00:06:56,080 --> 00:06:58,600
Lord Shen and I came to present gifts to Young Master Bai

134
00:06:58,600 --> 00:07:00,400
and Miss Song.

135
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:01,770
Marquis Bai.

136
00:07:02,840 --> 00:07:04,280
What's going on with Young Master Bai?

137
00:07:04,280 --> 00:07:05,200
My son

138
00:07:05,200 --> 00:07:06,880
is acting up a bit.

139
00:07:06,880 --> 00:07:08,640
I'm teaching him a lesson.

140
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:10,960
Bai Manchuan.

141
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:13,880
Are you dissatisfied with this marriage?

142
00:07:13,880 --> 00:07:15,200
If you don't agree,

143
00:07:15,200 --> 00:07:16,360
speak up now.

144
00:07:16,360 --> 00:07:19,080
Before it's too late.

145
00:07:20,640 --> 00:07:21,170
Untie me.

146
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:22,960
I...

147
00:07:23,000 --> 00:07:23,760
You what?

148
00:07:25,880 --> 00:07:27,800
I sincerely want to marry Song Xuan.

149
00:07:27,800 --> 00:07:29,320
Prime Minister Shen need not worry.

150
00:07:29,320 --> 00:07:30,360
What are you waiting for?

151
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:31,560
Untie me!

152
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:34,450
Please, Your Highness.

153
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:41,200
The bride is here!

154
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:50,570
Greetings, Your Highness.

155
00:07:59,200 --> 00:08:01,000
That scoundrel is setting us up.

156
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:06,410
Marquis Bai.

157
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:08,560
What is going on?

158
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:10,220
Your Highness.

159
00:08:11,080 --> 00:08:12,120
I am guilty.

160
00:08:12,840 --> 00:08:13,680
Third Prince.

161
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:15,360
Let us return to the palace immediately.

162
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:17,690
We must report this to the Emperor at once.

163
00:08:18,400 --> 00:08:21,640
The Third Prince is returning to the palace!

164
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:29,200
Son, I'm entrusting you to Song Xuan from now on.

165
00:08:29,560 --> 00:08:31,690
Father, didn't you say that backward?

166
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:33,480
Rest assured, my Lord.

167
00:08:33,640 --> 00:08:36,799
I will certainly discipline my husband well.

168
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:41,480
Come. Send the bride and groom to the bridal chamber.

169
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:48,160
I never thought my glorious reputation...

170
00:08:49,520 --> 00:08:52,080
...would end up in such a state today.

171
00:08:58,480 --> 00:09:01,520
Tonight is destined to be a sleepless night.

172
00:09:04,160 --> 00:09:05,960
Listen to me, Huanghuacai.

173
00:09:05,960 --> 00:09:07,200
Even if you possess my body,

174
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:08,800
you will never have my heart.

175
00:09:11,040 --> 00:09:14,240
Are you getting this wild on our wedding night?

176
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:17,240
It seems my husband knows quite a lot.

177
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:19,640
Linlang, bring the things here.

178
00:09:21,800 --> 00:09:22,600
Miss.

179
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:24,960
You pervert!

180
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:26,520
What exactly do you want to do?

181
00:09:26,520 --> 00:09:28,780
Master Bai, what are you thinking about?

182
00:09:28,800 --> 00:09:31,120
These are just ordinary items.

183
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:34,320
What kind of decent person calls these ordinary?

184
00:09:34,400 --> 00:09:37,720
You want to use these on me?

185
00:09:54,960 --> 00:09:57,120
Even if you use all of them on me,

186
00:09:57,160 --> 00:09:58,760
I will not yield.

187
00:09:58,880 --> 00:10:00,160
Just try it if you dare!

188
00:10:01,560 --> 00:10:03,290
My husband is overthinking it.

189
00:10:03,800 --> 00:10:06,320
I just want you to study hard.

190
00:10:06,360 --> 00:10:07,560
You did all this...

191
00:10:08,360 --> 00:10:10,040
...just to make me study?

192
00:10:10,080 --> 00:10:14,040
The Marquis said his son, Manchuan, has the makings of a Top Scholar.

193
00:10:14,080 --> 00:10:16,610
I must naturally fulfill the Marquis's wish.

194
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:20,160
So, you just need to study hard.

195
00:10:20,560 --> 00:10:21,720
What are you doing?

196
00:10:28,040 --> 00:10:30,840
Husband, for the sake of our future...

197
00:10:34,400 --> 00:10:35,920
The wedding night is precious.

198
00:10:35,920 --> 00:10:38,920
Are you sure you want to discuss this right now?

199
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,120
Mencius said,

200
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:46,760
'To nourish the heart, there is nothing better than having few desires.'

201
00:10:46,760 --> 00:10:47,690
What do you mean?

202
00:10:49,160 --> 00:10:52,080
Until you pass the imperial examination,

203
00:10:53,480 --> 00:10:55,540
it is better to practice abstinence.

204
00:10:56,160 --> 00:10:57,040
Ouch, ouch, ouch!

205
00:10:57,040 --> 00:10:58,000
Let go! Let go!

206
00:10:59,960 --> 00:11:00,840
You... you...

207
00:11:04,680 --> 00:11:06,600
Just so I can have a grandson sooner,

208
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:08,160
Manchuan is certainly working hard.
